PDF File → extractTextFromPdf → Plain Text → saveDocument → localStorage
                                    ↓
                          Document {id, name, text, pdfData, ...}
                                    ↓
                          generateQuizFromText → Gemini API
                                    ↓
                          parseQuizText → Questions Array
                                    ↓
                          saveQuiz → localStorage
                                    ↓
                          Quiz {id, questions[], score, difficulty, ...}
                                    ↓
                          QuizTakePage → User answers
                                    ↓
                          handleSubmitQuiz → Compare answers
                                    ↓
                          Updated Quiz + userAnswers → localStorage
                                    ↓
                          QuizResultPage → Display results with all options



